title: Ep. 83 "Is Drake Coming" ft. @thepsychicyogi
description:
This week we invited a psychic, healer, and lightworker to have some cocktails and talk COCKTALES with us. The lights were flickering, so Ms. Kisha Lee definitely was no joke. We had a million questions but all we really wanted to know was if Drake was coming and if we're going to be rich lol!
